issue.title: 新增集群运行时使用的containerd会部署失败
issue.body:
新增集群时，使用的k8s 1.26版本，runtime是containerd。生成的部署命令中不存在运行的环境变量增加，会导致部署失败。
建议增加一个容器运行时的选择，保证变量能够改变。--set operator.env[3].name=CONTAINER_RUNTIME --set operator.env[3].value=containerd

comment.body:
> Bot detected the issue body's language is not English, translate it automatically. 👯👭🏻🧑‍🤝‍🧑👫🧑🏿‍🤝‍🧑🏻👩🏾‍🤝‍👨🏿👬🏿      
----  
**Title:** The deployment of containerd used when adding a new cluster will fail    

When adding a new cluster, use k8s version 1.26 and the runtime is containerd. If there are no running environment variables in the generated deployment command, the deployment will fail.
It is recommended to add a container runtime option to ensure that variables can be changed. --set operator.env[3].name=CONTAINER_RUNTIME --set operator.env[3].value=containerd

issue.title: 对接集群多次出现通信异常的情况，始终无法恢复
issue.body:
![image](https://github.com/goodrain/rainbond/assets/61927670/0c1d313c-047c-4520-9b92-edc8104fce1b)
对接集群多次出现通信异常的情况，始终无法恢复，只能通过删除集群后再对接解决，如果部署集群部署了大量应用，无法恢复通信，就会存在巨大隐患。
日志出现过以下异常
![image](https://github.com/goodrain/rainbond/assets/61927670/a3d6425f-c978-4419-8c33-8cef7a1f178d)
对接集群中的rbd-api服务也无法重启

comment.body:
> Bot detected the issue body's language is not English, translate it automatically. 👯👭🏻🧑‍🤝‍🧑👫🧑🏿‍🤝‍🧑🏻👩🏾‍🤝‍👨🏿👬🏿         
----    
Is there an antecedent? The problem cannot be seen just from the communication abnormality, such as whether the IP changed after the server was restarted; or rbd-api did not start successfully; cluster network problems; and other factors that may cause it, you can follow [Troubleshooting Communication Abnormalities] Document](https://www.rainbond.com/docs/troubleshooting/use/cluster-connect/) Check it step by step. If you have any problems, you can continue to communicate in this issues, but it will be solved faster if you ask in the WeChat group.

issue.title: 对接集群多次出现通信异常的情况，始终无法恢复
issue.body:
![image](https://github.com/goodrain/rainbond/assets/61927670/0c1d313c-047c-4520-9b92-edc8104fce1b)
对接集群多次出现通信异常的情况，始终无法恢复，只能通过删除集群后再对接解决，如果部署集群部署了大量应用，无法恢复通信，就会存在巨大隐患。
日志出现过以下异常
![image](https://github.com/goodrain/rainbond/assets/61927670/a3d6425f-c978-4419-8c33-8cef7a1f178d)
对接集群中的rbd-api服务也无法重启

comment.body: 是否有前因呢，光从通信异常看不出来问题，比如 服务器是否重启后 ip 变更；或者 rbd-api 未启动成功；集群网络问题；等等因可能导致的因素，你可以按照 [通信异常排查文档](https://www.rainbond.com/docs/troubleshooting/use/cluster-connect/) 逐步排查一下，如果有问题可以继续在此issues沟通，不过在微信群问的话解决起来会快一些。
